  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Riders In has a relaxed, welcoming philosophy which you can feel as soon as you walk through the doors. The hotel owners believe in enjoying life to the fullest which is what Sölden is all about. The hotel mixes traditional Tyrolean design with stylish interior design. </p>
<h2>Bar &amp; restaurant</h2>
<p>You are just 100 metres from the centre of Sölden and the hotel has its own popular Pfiff bar where you can continue on the après after a day on the slopes. </p>
<p>The hotel restaurant dinner is a buffet with a wide variety of options. Staff are always on hand to advise on a great wine pairing.</p>
<p>The Riders In is available on Half-Board or Bed &amp; Breakfast.</p>
<h2>Wellness area</h2>
<p>The wellness area has a sleek modern design and includes a heated indoor pool, whirlpool, steam room, Finnish sauna, Kneipp foot spa pool, ice grotto, and fitness room.</p>
<p>If you need even more relaxation, guests receive a 10% discount to the Aqua Dome, with <span>50,000 m² of swimming, saunas, and wellness facilities.</span></p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Riders In the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
