  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Double</strong> rooms have a bath or shower, WC, and can sleep up to three using a single sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Double</strong> rooms are decorated with a more contemporary feel. They have a shower and can sleep three.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Family</strong> rooms have a bath or shower and balcony. They can sleep four using a double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Family Superior</strong> rooms are decorated with a contemporary feel. They can sleep four using a double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Einzel</strong> single rooms have a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Einzel</strong> single rooms are slightly large, have a shower and are decorated with a contemporary feel.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
